# 4. Architectural Style

The platform follows a Hybrid Architecture.

Combining

Layered Architecture

+

Service Oriented Architecture

+

Event Driven Processing

+

AI Orchestration

Why?

Layered Architecture

Simplifies business logic.

Service Oriented

Allows future microservices.

Event Driven

Moves heavy work to queues.

AI Orchestration

Allows multiple AI agents.

