# 14. Summary

This architecture establishes a modular, cloud-native foundation for the Developer Intelligence Platform. By separating concerns across frontend, backend, AI orchestration, and asynchronous workers, the system remains scalable, maintainable, and ready for future expansion into enterprise hiring, educational analytics, and developer intelligence products.